title: NASA's Crew-11 astronauts to discuss medical evacuation from International Space Station today: Watch it live
description: The four astronauts of SpaceX's Crew-11 mission will discuss their shorter-than-expected stay aboard the International Space Station today (Jan. 21), and you can watch it live.
